    <div class="card_column">
      <div class="card_title">
        Zephair E-Commerce
      </div>
      <div class="card_tags">
        <span class="card_tag">PHP</span>
        <span class="card_tag">Bitcoin</span>
        <span class="card_tag">Web design</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card_description">
        <p class="card_description_paragraph">
          The Zephair E-commerce website was a project for one of my courses at the University of Virginia, CS 4753: E-Commerce Technologies. My team built an online store for our company's product - canned air - that allowed customers to register, browse the store, add items to cart, pay with bitcoin, leave reviews, and more.
        </p>
        <p class="right">
          <a href='/projects/zephair'>Read more...</a>
        </p>
      </div>
